    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You touch a target with a device you\u2019re holding that uses electricity, requiring a melee attack against the target\u2019s EAC. Alternatively, you can instead touch an electrical device a target is wearing (or a target that is an electrical device, such as a robot) with your hand, gaining a +2 bonus to your attack roll. Either way, if your attack hits, the electrical device surges out of control, dealing 4d6 electricity damage to your target.<br><br>Casting this spell doesn\u2019t provoke attacks of opportunity.</p>"
